# Tera Filters Reference

Tera supports many built-in filters for transforming variables.

## String Case Filters

- `snake`: Convert to snake_case
- `pascal`: Convert to PascalCase
- `camel`: Convert to camelCase
- `ucfirst`: Capitalize first character
- `upper`: Convert to UPPERCASE
- `lower`: Convert to lowercase

## Usage

Apply filters with the pipe operator:

{% raw %}
```tera
{{ variable_name | filter_name }}
```
{% endraw %}

## Examples

{% raw %}
```tera
{{ "UserService" | snake }}       // user_service
{{ "user_service" | pascal }}     // UserService
{{ "hello" | ucfirst }}           // Hello
{{ "HELLO" | lower }}             // hello
```
{% endraw %}
